<section xmlns="http://xml.house.gov/schemas/uslm/1.0" style="-uslm-lc:I80" id="idbf0e0165-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s10108"><num value="10108">§ 10108.</num><heading> Applicability to transportation</heading><content>
<p style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">Nothing in this chapter shall be construed to affect Federal, State, or local laws pertaining to the transportation of spent nuclear fuel or high-level radioactive waste.</p>
</content><sourceCredit id="idbf0e0166-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa">(<ref href="/us/pl/97/425/s9">Pub. L. 97–425, § 9</ref>, <date date="1983-01-07">Jan. 7, 1983</date>, <ref href="/us/stat/96/2206">96 Stat. 2206</ref>.)</sourceCredit>
</section>
